body: "CONTEXT: pm-cli is a universal, agent-optimized, git-native project management CLI. DECISION: The product north star is 'project management = context management' — pm ships PM primitives via the pm SDK so any project can fully customize and optimize it; the tracker is the durable, shared context store for humans and coding agents across Claude Code, Codex, Cursor, and bare CLI. CONSEQUENCES: features are judged by whether they make project context more complete, organized, and discoverable; agent-ergonomics and determinism are first-class; the tracker must be a LIVING map (forward backlog + decisions), not only a completed-work log. EVIDENCE: README.md, AGENTS.md, PRD.md, docs/ARCHITECTURE.md; this audit (pm-w7f2) seeded the forward layer."
